   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Educate in Competences 3750 Taxi Drivers in Bogota</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Fundacion Ciudad y Transporte plans to provide 15 free training programs throughout the year to educate at least 3.750 taxi drivers in Bogota City, in citizenship and labor competences, seeking for the improvement of their educational conditions and the enhancement of their quality of life and service. This project will help them to face efficiently the new challenges that the globalization has brought to the cities this new century and to professionalize their field.</narrative>
  </description>
